Thanks. And this has like many part answer. So first and foremost, let's start with the part on Rachel.

00:03:12.119 --> 00:03:18.600
You're right. And I'm glad you remember. That's also my first meeting that I met her with Rachel.

00:03:18.600 --> 00:03:27.160
