00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:29.600
So I pushed back and I said, no, we're doing this. And I think that has therefore in the next year and a half to come,

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:36.760
has become one of the instrumental pieces of why I think this change management part is going so well internally.

00:04:36.760 --> 00:04:41.880
