00:09:19.359 --> 00:09:26.479
and one of them was like, have you experienced an open source transition at work from closed source to open source?

00:09:26.479 --> 00:09:30.280
Less than half said yes, more than half said no.

00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:34.599
