00:54:17.360 --> 00:54:19.760
That's a team in the US National Women's Soccer League.

00:54:19.760 --> 00:54:20.879
So I'm really excited about that.

00:54:20.879 --> 00:54:22.800
She's going to talk all about working out loud,

00:54:22.800 --> 00:54:24.320
which is one of my favorite topics.

00:54:24.320 --> 00:54:25.439
Join us next week.

00:54:25.439 --> 00:54:27.919
I will see you in the Discord server, everybody,

00:54:27.919 --> 00:54:31.040
between now and then, and on Blue Sky and LinkedIn.

00:54:31.040 --> 00:54:32.399
Judy, thank you so much for hanging out with us.

00:54:32.399 --> 00:54:33.360
Thank you so much, guys.

00:54:33.360 --> 00:54:34.719
It was really, really a pleasure.

00:54:34.719 --> 00:54:35.280
Thanks a lot.

00:54:35.840 --> 00:54:38.239
Go find Judy on LinkedIn and say hello.

00:54:38.239 --> 00:54:39.199
Goodbye, everybody.

00:54:39.199 --> 00:54:40.800
